### 读取指定设备位号值
#driver/read
POST http://localhost:8604/driver/read
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

[
  {
    "deviceId": 1,
    "pointId": 1
  }
]


### 写入指定设备位号值
#driver/write
POST http://localhost:8604/driver/write
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

[
  {
    "deviceId": 1,
    "pointId": 1,
    "value": "23"
  }
]

###